,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前每逢有朋友生日，果晚就一齊去唱k，假日撞正人多唱幾粒鐘就趕你走，位位幾舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:59:22.000Z","msg":"貴到仆街<br />\n十條友一間房仔又係唱果一陣<br />\n斷人頭計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b803ec59b9fd8e08e5b96e19d10771c7c144f0","tid":2516197,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:59:59.000Z","msg":"食物好撚難食，比貴一倍去red mr都唔去neway<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1e9913f9ccafdf71592ce34a8e6ce9c30fec26","tid":2516197,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60a1db516a144e5bb01791882fb9887bf092e556","tid":2516197,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"afdc02ee45eff1728992896879640a710ff750dc","tid":2516197,"uid":371001,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:27:11.000Z","msg":"講真嗰句<br />\n新少少嘅英文歌都冇<br />\n點引客..<br />\n廣東歌都係<br />\n<br />\n所以通常入neway都係一個mic播youtube karaoke<br />\n然後唱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"好多歌都冇的確係一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:00:17.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅歌曲下架 K房不減價<br />\n更新時間 (HKT): <span class=\"red\"><strong>2018.10.31 05:20</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】判詞一出，《蘋果》記者昨傍晚到觀塘的Neway分店以顧客身份查詢，職員確認，陳奕迅等環球唱片歌手的K歌現已下架，「想唱都冇辦法」，但不會因無法提供部份歌曲而減價。環球回應裁決稱「唔會鬥氣」，願意冰釋前嫌，「公司打開門做生意，如果價錢合理，可以傾返合作」。<br />\n<br />\n記者昨向分店接待處職員查詢：「有冇得唱陳奕迅？好似話𠵱家冇得唱？」職員回應謂：「係呀！有啲環球（唱片）嘅歌，我哋落咗架。」但指不會因此減價，每位顧客依然收費約200元，包兩杯飲品。<br />\n<br />\n張學友歌全非原唱<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：Neway被裁侵權 7日內刪K歌 須賠環球損失兼付訟費<br />\n記者入房後點歌，發現歌手目錄中仍然有環球的歌手選項，如張學友、陳慧琳及陳奕迅等，但發現環球歌手的MV大多是他人演唱的版本。如張學友有62首歌，全部不是學友所唱的版本，而是其他歌星唱，《吻別》是劉德華版、《李香蘭》是呂方演唱會版，《頭髮亂了》則是吳浩康唱；而陳慧琳24首亦同樣全非陳唱的版本，《花花宇宙》是鄭秀文版。至於陳奕迅則一半一半，其舊公司的《單車》、《K歌之王》有Eason版本，但環球新歌則全部欠奉。<br />\n<br />\n法政匯思召集人蔡騏指出，Neway等被告公司除要賠償侵權費外，亦需與環球重新洽商歌曲再上架的版權費，即使Neway願意出更高價錢，環球仍可拒絕讓歌曲上架。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姜偉康、鄭語霆"},{"pid":"d43af9f327ba84d33165ef0bae10c46002dfcde2","tid":2516197,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:00:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20181031/7YVWN5DHMX5JFQKVS6N4NFPR5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20181031%2F7YVWN5DHMX5JFQKVS6N4NFPR5A%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK1xDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=93315cc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20181031%2F7YVWN5DHMX5JFQKVS6N4NFPR5A%2F&h=00f9b074\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20181031/7YVWN5DHMX5JFQKVS6N4NFPR5A/</a>"},{"pid":"4f9dce948d450785a2070a31dea0cad3f8d00b85","tid":2516197,"uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ed5f69ced5f5d7e9c2ec3841f46a9f8280fa0bd4","tid":2516197,"uid":5725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a218b48915d5c57a5992fa39ed482ab322b78761","tid":2516197,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前每逢有朋友生日，果晚就一齊去唱k，假日撞正人多唱幾粒鐘就趕你走，位位幾舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:59:22.000Z","msg":"貴到仆街<br />\n十條友一間房仔又係唱果一陣<br />\n斷人頭計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"得兩杯凍飲同垃圾nuts,有人生日送多個蛋糕，首生日歌又長又冇得cut阻撚7住唱k"},{"pid":"c4c6548443807070a4302598b6ef825b4e594bed","tid":2516197,"uid":244391,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f9dce948d450785a2070a31dea0cad3f8d00b85","tid":2516197,"uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"